{"tid":18014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲傭涉掌摑3歲少主　9歲姊手機拍下罪證","createTime":"2016-12-02T05:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T05:28:34.000Z","uid":22680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27d02123f416c9bb43aa471a07647c2c42afee45","tid":18014,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:16:59.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】牛頭角花園大廈揭發懷疑外傭虐兒案，一名菲傭涉嫌掌摑3歲少主被捕。掌摑過程剛好被少主9歲姊姊的手機拍下，成為罪證。<br />\n　　案發於上月30日，21歲的菲傭帶同9歲及3歲的少主人乘巴士，從港島東區返回花園大廈玉蓮臺寓所。期間，3歲少主在車上懷疑頑皮不聽管教，菲傭勸止不果後掌摑對方。<br />\n　　由於姊姊剛好取出手機拍攝沿途風景，也拍下案發經過。女童回家後並無向父母告狀，但到昨日，女童母親終發現短片，送男童入院檢驗，並於今日凌晨1時許報警。<br />\n　　警方到玉蓮臺3座將涉案菲傭帶返警署扣查，暫列虐兒案處理，交刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8F%B2%E5%82%AD%E6%B6%89%E6%8E%8C%E6%91%913%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E4%B8%BB-9%E6%AD%B2%E5%A7%8A%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%8B%8D%E4%B8%8B%E7%BD%AA%E8%AD%89-015100464.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%258F%25B2%25E5%2582%25AD%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%258E%258C%25E6%2591%25913%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB-9%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A7%258A%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%258B%258D%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E8%25AD%2589-015100464.html&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=601c87bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8F%B2%E5%82%AD%E6%B6%89%E6%8E%8C%E6%91%913%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E4%B8%BB-9%E6%AD%B2%E5%A7%8A%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%8B%8D%E4%B8%8B%E7%BD%AA%E8%AD%89-015100464.html</a><br />\n<br />\n家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b311ab5915693eb4affb1014b47e11403daf7ae6","tid":18014,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:17:51.000Z","msg":"係咪前排瘋傳過段<br />\n打到bb出唔到聲 係梳化上面個段"},{"pid":"b77ea042f24b0f61727d940e292b6e12e1d2968c","tid":18014,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:19:23.00